# Worker topology: source config is tracked (container.json / CLAUDE.local.md /
# AGENTS.md). Spawn-time generated artifacts are not — .claude-fragments/ is
# composed per-spawn, CLAUDE.md is the generated @import list, and
# .claude-shared.md is a container-path symlink that is broken on the host.
groups/*/.claude-fragments/
groups/*/.claude-shared.md
groups/*/CLAUDE.md
# Worker runtime artifacts (camera frames, skill scratch output).
groups/**/*.jpg
groups/**/*.jpeg
groups/**/*.png

container/agent-runner/node_modules/

# Perf benchmark raw output — local-only clutter, not source.
perf-results-raw*.json

*.sqlite
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.pid

